  1.  Prerequisites

  This OS template requires Virtuozzo version 4.0.0 or later with a
  vzpkgenv41 version 4.0.0-38 or later, kernel version 2.6.18-028stab059.3
  or later and rpm2vzrpm version 4.2.1-4.2.42 or later.

  Please note that this template has some requirements to Container resources
  which are covered by sample Container config named 'vps.basic' or 'unlimited'.
  In addition to that, the following limits should be raised:

  privvmpages shall be set to 35,000 or more.


